data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!  Welcome to this "like new" home in the desirable Forest Parks neighborhood.  New oven, microwave, disposal. HVAC, roof, garage doors, windows, water heater and sprinkler system all within the last 5 years. Plantation shutters in home, custom EcoView windows with transferable warranty, and hardwood floors. Enjoy 12 ft. vaulted ceilings in LR with gas FP and formal DR, the eat-in kitchen has custom cabinets, granite countertops, and KitchenAid stainless steel appliances.  Larger than usual MBR with 9 ft. vaulted ceilings with two closets, huge primary BA with double sink vanity, separate shower and jetted tub plus two carpeted BR and full BA all on main level. Downstairs has two more large BRs, bonus room, full bath, laundry area and two car garage.  Ample closet space. Freshly painted exterior. A backyard oasis for entertaining includes covered, tiled upper deck with ceiling fan and lower fenced patio with wrought iron fencing.  GORGEOUS!  Very convenient location!
